dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Created and populated reference name field. 2. Fixed double space errors in Admin3 names "SAN FCO. DE SIGSIPAMBA" and "ISLA SANTA MARÍA (FLOREANA) (CAB. EN PTO. VELASCO IBARRA)". 3. Admin1-3 names converted to Proper Case. 4. Fixed 55 multipart sliver errors 5. Fixed long sliver extending beyond the bottom polygon of "Puerto Ayora".
The following was found by ITOS but not addressed in this version: 1. The parentheses in some names suggest the presence of alternate names that should be separated and placed in AltName fields
